name: Tidal
description: Artist: Laura Rafferty - Medium: Mixed Media - Year: 2020 - Like the ocean, waves of grief and joy flow over me. In the tidal pools, I swim with my emotions and let them wash out to sea on the next low tide. - This was an expression of my loss of loved ones and deep sadness that overcame me from isolation and loneliness during the pandemic. Creating art helped me heal and move forward.
